                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270111-205-off1138 t18270111-205-cd1139"></join>, 1 basket, value 8d.; 6 1/2lbs. of pork, value 4s. 4d.; 5lbs. of lard, value 4s.; 1lb. of filbert-nuts, value 6d.; 1 cake, value 6d.; 1 1/2 yard of lace, value 6d., and 4 shillings
