                     <interp inst="t18270111-205-person1912" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at Shenfield, Essex. I gave a basket to Mr. Spinks, to take to town, containing this property, on the 28th of December.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270111-205-person1913">
                  JOHN 
                  ROE
